    <item>
      <title>由于日元承压，日本央行在常规操作中削减债券购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/boj-trims-bond-buying-in-regular-operation-amid-pressure-on-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行周一提出在常规操作中购买比 4 月 24 日更少数量的政府债券，以减少其在该国债务市场的份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/boj-trims-bond-buying-in-regular-operation-amid-pressure-on-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 01:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲对降息的厌恶导致新兴市场债券投资者望而却步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bond-traders-betting-on-fed-cuts-have-reason-to-overlook-em-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与全球同行相比，新兴亚洲债券的上涨空间可能较小，因为该地区央行不太可能采取大幅降息措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bond-traders-betting-on-fed-cuts-have-reason-to-overlook-em-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 01:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博新能源财经称，日本今年可能会重启世界上最大的核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/japan-s-tepco-will-restart-biggest-nuclear-plant-this-year-bnef-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新能源财经报道，世界上最大的核电站可能会在停产十多年后于今年恢复发电，这是技术复兴的一部分，将有助于降低日本的电力成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/japan-s-tepco-will-restart-biggest-nuclear-plant-this-year-bnef-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称中国计划周五首次出售超长期中央债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-to-hold-meeting-on-138-billion-ultra-long-debt-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国计划于周五开始发售第一批1万亿元人民币（合1,380亿美元）的超长期特别主权债券，以筹集资金支持世界第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-to-hold-meeting-on-138-billion-ultra-long-debt-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 00:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
